::Striker::

Striker looks at Spears as she takes his arm (I think he was in beast mode, 
but that's ok.). He shakes himself out of his trance. It was pointless, being 
sad at a lost valley didn't do any good, and it did do harm to morale. He 
grins at Spears.

"Well, that didn't go exacty as planned, did it?" he asks, a joking tone in 
his voice.
